data.meta_description: Download this stock image: Dec. 12, 1957 - Lilli Palmer Flies in with Her New Husband. Actress Lilli Palmer a former wife of Rex Harrison - flew into London last night with the man she married in September... Argentinian actor Carlos Thompson. It is their first visit to Britain together and they are to spend Christmas with Lilli's sister, Mrs. Hilde Schnitzer. - E0R27C from Alamy's library of millions of high resolution stock photos, illustrations and vectors.
